description: Product Description 25 Litre Recycled Euro Plastic Stacking Container Made from 100% recycled polypropylene material - The ideal environmental solution to reduce the global impact of plastics. High load capacity - Suitable for even the most heavy duty applications. These containers are not food grade certified. Smooth bases for use on conveyors and easily cleaned. Open Handholes on ends for easy manual handling when loaded. Designed to European Container dimensions – Fit 10 per layer on 1200 x 1000mm on UK pallet or 8 per layer on 1200 x 800mm Euro Pallet. Will inter-stack with all euro containers from major manufacturers. Accessories available to make your life easier - Dollies for transportation, lids to keep contents secure and label holders for easy identification. Capacity: 25 Litres Load Capacity: 20kg / 120kg Stacked Weight: 1.45 Kg Dimensions (External): L 400 x W 300 x H 290 mm Dimensions (Internal): L 355 x W 255 x H 280 mm
